---

PrivateCore AI integrates with and references several independent
open-source projects, including (in alphabetical order):

  - Ansible (GPLv3) — https://www.ansible.com/
  - Chroma (Apache-2.0) — https://www.trychroma.com/
  - Docker (Apache-2.0) — https://www.docker.com/
  - Immich (AGPLv3) — https://immich.app/
  - Intel OpenVINO (Apache-2.0) — https://openvino.ai/
  - IPEX-LLM (Apache-2.0) — https://github.com/intel-analytics/ipex-llm
  - llama.cpp (MIT) — https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp
  - Nextcloud (AGPLv3) — https://nextcloud.com/
  - Ollama (MIT) — https://ollama.com/
  - Paperless-ngx (GPLv3) — https://docs.paperless-ngx.com/
  - Proxmox VE (AGPLv3) — https://www.proxmox.com/
  - Qdrant (Apache-2.0) — https://qdrant.tech/
  - TrueNAS Scale (combined: GPLv2/v3, BSD, Apache-2.0) — https://www.truenas.com/

These projects are NOT included in this repository. PrivateCore AI
provides deployment automation, configuration, and integration code
that orchestrates these projects in the user's own environment. Each
project is governed by its own licence. Trademarks belong to their
respective owners.
